基本可视化

dat <- read.csv("C:/Users/Lenovo/Desktop/train_HR.csv")
dat <- data.frame(dat,number=1:nrow(dat))
set.seed(0)
train_index = caret::createDataPartition(dat$number, times = 1, p = 0.7, list = FALSE)
dat_train = dat[train_index[,1],]
dat_train <- dat_train[,-13]
dat_test = dat[-train_index[,1],]
dat_test <- dat_test[,-13]
formu = as.factor(is_promoted) ~ .
rm(dat)
#随机森林
library(ranger)
fit_rf = ranger(formu, data = dat_train, num.trees = 500, mtry = NULL)

pred_rf = predict(fit_rf, dat_test)
library("pROC")
roc(pred_rf$predictions, dat_test$is_promoted, plot=TRUE, print.thres=TRUE, print.auc=TRUE)

## 
## Call:
## roc.default(response = pred_rf$predictions, predictor = dat_test$is_promoted,     plot = TRUE, print.thres = TRUE, print.auc = TRUE)
## 
## Data: dat_test$is_promoted in 14214 controls (pred_rf$predictions 0) < 382 cases (pred_rf$predictions 1).
## Area under the curve: 0.9263
#LIME图绘制
explainer <- lime(dat_train,fit_rf)
e <- explain(dat_test[1:2,],explainer,n_labels = 1,n_features=4)
plot_features(e)

#confusionMatrix(pred_rf$predictions,as.factor(dat_test$is_promoted))
dat1 <- table(pred_rf$predictions,dat_test$is_promoted)
dimnames(dat1) <- list(c('预测为0','预测为1'),c('实际为0','实际为1'))
dat1 <- cbind(dat1,总计=apply(dat1, 1, sum))#增加行和
#增加列和并输出表
rbind(dat1,总计=apply(dat1, 2, sum))
